posts.title: Things we learned from the second would-be assassins Twitter...
posts.content:
-He @'d many prominent people on Twitter, including Seth Rogen, Sean Penn, Angelina Jolie, James Franco, Nikki Haley, Joe Biden, and most Recently, Kamala Harris.

-He was the head of the volunteer fighter recruitment for Ukraine and supposedly spent several months in Ukraine as a volunteer combatant against Russia.

-He tried to buy a used SpaceX rocket from Elon Musk, to use to blow up "Putin's Black Sea mansion bunker".

-He is a big fan of N. Korea and Kim Jong Un.

-He offered Haiti 1,000 NATO trained Afghan mercenaries for $200 a month per fighter to Frantz Elbe, the director of Haiti’s National Police, who was ousted by Haiti leaders a few months ago for not doing enough to combat the gangs in Haiti, and also contacted other high level Haiti officials. If serious, this adds another degree to the assassination attempt, since it would mean this individual has had actual large groups of Ukraine employed mercenaries under his command. Furthermore, he even contacted US senators such as Diane Feinstein for the same reason; to offer NATO trained Afghani mercenaries for Haiti.

-He offered thousands of Afghan mercenaries to Taiwan for defense, again, for $200 per month per fighter. He contacted several officials in Taiwan offering mercenaries, and went as far as to say "We should be preparing for war", which is all very much a federal crime. In total, he offered Taiwan over 50,000 NATO trained Afghani mercenaries, and visited Taiwan to lobby his mercenaries to them.

-He gave mixed messages about his feelings toward Nikki Haley. He hated her later on, but when Vivek Ramaswamy was running, he said he needed to stay on the ballot to the end, seeming in support of him. At an earlier point he scolded Vivek for wearing the same jacket every day. Overall he seemed to be a fan of Vivek and Nikki, but it really seemed like he was trolling and hoping that they could knock Trump off the ballot.

-He contacted the Secretary of Defense, Lloyd Austin, on Twitter, asking for money for 10,000 Afghan soldiers in Ukraine, effectively openly operating as a mercenary group. He also contacted the Department of Defense to ask for help in getting thousands of NATO trained Afgani mercenaries to Taiwan. He also at one point said that the Pentagon had agreed to help him, and contacted various other Biden administration military officials, including Sec. Blinken.

-He's from Hawaii

-He individually contacted various bands such as Dave Mathews Band, Sting, Kings of Leon, Jack Johnson, U2, Bono and Bruno Mars to try to get them to do a Ukraine support song he wrote himself, titled "We are One".

-On 5-17-2022, he made a Tweet that said "Killing anywhere is extremely tragic". Irony much?

-He seemed to have interactions and/or affiliations with a group known as Project 2049.

-At times he also offered Syrian mercenaries along with Afghan mercenaries.

-He once said "We will not stop until Putin is dead and Moscow is a pile of rubble. I am in Ukraine and not leaving until Moscow gone". He was allegedly in Ukraine and left after being there for 8 months.

-He lobbied for nuclear weapons to be given back to Ukraine to "flatten Moscow and take all the resources".

-He contacted Zelensky on Twitter multiple times about buying all the weapons he could from anywhere in the world that would sell them. He told Zelensky "I do not want to die here in Kyiv next to you".

-He contacted the Minister of National Defense in Poland, offering to buy up their planes as an intermediary for Ukraine.

-He said on 3-15-2022, "The only way to end the war is to kill Putin in his bed at night".

-He contacted Tulsi Gabbard to tell her she's an idiot and that she should join Putin and Trump and be their third leg. He contacted her another time to say, "I am beginning to think you are just Crazy....I think you are a Republican and Trump nut at this point, that grey streak in your hair is soo stupid".

-He was a Tom Brady fan.

-He told Paula Newton from CNN that he is going to "fight and die for Ukraine".

-He told Pamela Brown from CNN that "this is WW3, why is the global community not doing more".

-He was "moved" by Lester Holt being emotionally shaken on a broadcast from 3-09-2022.

-On 2-27-2022, he messaged a person "@mllesookim", which seems to be a former CIA and DHS employee that operates in the Korean Peninsula, and is currently an analyst for "@RANDCorporation" think tank. He told them "You and I can go to North Korea and sit down with the foreign minister and end hostilities".

Guys I'm not even half way through analyzing the archive video of his tweets, this shit is wild. Check it out for yourself: https://patriots.win/p/1994yImJ16/x/c/4ZF9nr7mVmB?d=50

TLDR; He's a mouth foaming TDS sufferer and seems to have connections to the highest levels of officials in the Biden/Kamala administration, which seems to include direct funding from the Biden/Kamala administration, along with connections to various other agencies and governments, including CIA, DHS, Pentagon, Department of Defense, Ukraine, Poland, Taiwan, Afghanistan, Syria, and mercenary groups, and headed up the foreign fighter volunteer organization for Ukraine.
